title: Film blowing printing connect line set US-SJA50-YT(ASY)2600
title_uz: Polietilen rulonli plyonka ishlab chiqarish uchun ekstruder US-SJA50-YT(ASY)2600
title_ru: Экструдер для производства полиэтиленовой рулонной пленки US-SJA50-YT(ASY)2600
title_en: Film blowing printing connect line set US-SJA50-YT(ASY)2600
short_description: The difference of this US-SJA50-YT(ASY)2600 extruder from others is that this extruder package also includes a printing machine, which means that the film that comes out goes straight into the printing machine. The width of the product produced by the extruder and the maximum width of printing is 600 mm. The total power of the equipment is 28 kW, and the power of the main motor is 11 kW. The extruder is capable of producing up to 35 kg of film per hour. There are other models of this equipment in the description, and they differ in price and parameters.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-SJA50-YT(ASY)2600 esktruderning boshqalaridan farqi shuki, bu ekstruder to'plamida pechat qiladigan uskuna ham mavjud, ya'ni chiqqan plyonka birdaniga pechat qilish uskunasiga kirib ketaveradi. Ekstruder ishlab chiqargan mahsulot kengligi va pechat qilishning maksimal kengligi 600 mm. Uskunaning umumiy quvvati 28 kW, asosiy motor quvvati esa 11 kW. Ekstruder soatiga 35 kg gacha plyonka ishlab chiqarish imkoniyatiga ega. Tavsifda bu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham mavjud va ular narx va parametrlarda bir-biridan farq qiladi.

Ширина изделия, выпускаемого экструдером, и максимальная ширина печати составляет 600 мм. Суммарная мощность оборудования 28 кВт, мощность главного двигателя 11 кВт. Экструдер способен производить до 35 кг пленки в час. В описании есть и другие модели данного оборудования, и они отличаются по цене и параметрам.
